      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an impeccable standard. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a machine in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Meticulously inspected and preserved, it offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
