      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and its signature 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen is in concours condition, showcasing flawless factory paint and a meticulously preserved interior. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the individual throttle bodies are perfectly synchronized, and the M-DCT dual-clutch transmission delivers instantaneous, crisp gear changes. Critical preventative maintenance has been performed, including rod bearing replacement with VAC treated bearings and upgraded throttle actuators. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and remains as taut as the day it left Regensburg. Riding on unblemished ZCP competition wheels with fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires, this M3 represents the pinnacle of high-revving atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
